{ If White wants to play Nc3 next, this trade seems to be necessary. } 12...
Rxa7 13. Nc3 { The modern engines remain optimistic though. } 13... Nf4 14. Qe3
Nbxd3 15. Qxa7 Qg5 { Black starts a very dangerous attack. } 16. g3 Nh3+ 17.
Kg2 Ndxf2 18. Rf1 Ng4 19. Rae1 Qh5
{ The forced line is finished - the engines here announce complete equality, but you can judge for yourself. }
