10... Rxa7 11. c4 { The last attempt to set up the Maroczy Bind. } 11... d5
{ Black's response doesn't change. } 12. exd5 exd5 13. Rd1
{ The best practical chance for White - the last move has taken the ...dxc4 option away from Black. There is a similar position but with the white queen standing on e3, for some better circumstances. Here, Black's approach remains the same - close the center, although things are still not quite simple. }
13... d4
{ Black has to push the d-pawn forward - better sooner than later. Now White has numerous ways how to challenge the d4-pawn but Black should have enough resources to equalize. }
