{ The position is not out of life yet - even though the d4-pawn will fall now, Black will always have good counterplay due to the powerful light-squared bishop. }
17... hxg6 18. Rad1 Re8
{ Black starts to make the preparations to give up the d4-pawn under the best circumstances. And they are - activate your pieces! }
19. Qf1 Qf6 20. Ncxd4 Ne5
{ Finally, White has achieved what he wanted but Black is incredibly active. }
