13. Bxe5 dxe5
{ Black already is thinking about ...b5 next, so White needs to do something. }
14. g4 { To get the better chances, White has to play very aggressively. }
14... Rd8 15. Qe3 Bd7 { No unnecessary trades. } 16. g5 Ne8 17. Kb1 Ne7
{ The position is very complex - White's attack on the kingside might finish before it gets started, leaving several weaknesses behind. }
