{ The pawn on e5 is under attack - what should White do? } 8. Qe2
{ 8.Qd5  e6  9.Qe4  Bg7  this doesn't change much from Black's perspective. }
8... Bg7 9. c4 Qa5+
{ White doesn't have a satisfactory continuation here - Black's ...d6 is incoming. }
