8. Nd2 O-O 9. O-O Na6
{ In the spirit of the position - Black is thinking about the next moves ...Nb4 or ...Ng6 and then see what happens in the game. If Black would play the immediate  9...d5  , then White can close the center with  10.e5  and an interesting French Defense setup. There's no need to close the center. }
