13... f6 14. exf6 gxf6 15. h5 O-O-O
{ We're not even sure what kind of sign this move deserves! Probably something like !?! for the bravery and imagination. On a serious note, Black's attack looks very strong. }
16. hxg6 hxg6 17. Re1 e5
{ Something is about to happen at the h-file.   The game could continue this way:  18.Nbd2  Be7  19.Ne4  Rh7  20.Kf1  g5  White will have to be very careful. }
