{ Unless there's a direct gain, don't trade the knight on d4 yourself, this will only strengthen White's control over the d4-square. Instead, Black is interested to allow White to take on c6  @@StartBracket@@or e6 on some occasions@@EndBracket@@, thus strengthening the d5-pawn with another pawn. }
