13... Be4 14. Bg2
{ The position again tends to calm down - it depends on the players, how sharp the game are they looking for! }
14... Qa5 15. Bxf6 gxf6 16. Bxe4 dxe4 17. Qxf6 Rae8
{ The game is still very unclear but at least there's no immediate perpetual check. }
