7. Nc3
{ If White so badly insists on playing the gambit, why not? A smart player knows when to pick a fight. }
7... Nxe4
{ Black accepts the gambit and the subsequent endgame, but makes an important piece trade in the process. If you have a look at the alternative continuation that you had before, you'll see this is an improved version for Black. }
