{ Black needs to be careful since this move comes with the e5 and Ne4 threats. }
13... Nh5 14. Qf3 g6
{ Black could already repeat the position with  14...Nf6  . } 15. g4 Nf6 16. g5
Nh5
{ White probably wants to execute the Ne2-g3 plan and then do something with the open h-file, but Black is pretty fast with his counterplay on the queenside. There's no need to castle yet. }
