12... h5 13. Qf3 h4 { Black is thinking about ...f5 and ...Nf6 next. } 14. Bf4
{ With this trade, White accepts that he is slightly worse and is asking for a way out. }
14... hxg3 15. hxg3 Bxf4 16. Qxf4 Qxf4 17. gxf4 Rh4
{ Black's chances look better. } *

