11. c4 { White can keep the pawn but this will be a great gambit for Black! }
11... h6 12. Nh3 Bd6
{ Black takes away some retreat squares from the white queen. } 13. Nc3 O-O
{ Black has a wonderful compensation for the pawn and even more. } *

