{ Since Black's ...Ba6 is a serious positional threat, White has to act quickly. }
14. e5 Nh7 15. Bxe7 Qxe7
{ The black knight on h7 feels awkward but White can't exploit it as the position is closed and the only way to open up the position is with the f5 push, which would give the Black knight the g5-square. If nothing dramatic happens, the knight will eventually come back to the game via the f8-square. }
