{ Black started to take over the game as White completely lost the game thread. If not f4, then what else?   22.f3  Nc4  23.Rd3  Rc7  24.h4  g4!  25.f4  Rb8  . Black's initiative was already in full swing - White didn't hold for long in Kiuttu, R. @@StartBracket@@2324@@EndBracket@@ - Neiksans, A. @@StartBracket@@2535@@EndBracket@@ FIN-chT 1213 2012. }
