19. f4 { Did Black just blunder? } 19... Nxf4
{ No, that's a sacrifice on purpose! } 20. Bxf4 Nd3+ 21. Bxd3 Qxf4
{ Black has a very strong initiative while the White knight on b6 is helpless to join the defenders. }
22. Qd2 Bh4+ 23. Kd1
