{ Pichot, A. @@StartBracket@@2630@@EndBracket@@ - Zubov, A. @@StartBracket@@2598@@EndBracket@@ chess.com Titled Tuesday 2021. This logical move receives an unexpected punishment. }
13... Nxd4 14. Qxd4 d5
{ White misses another shot - now Black's advantage is close to decisive. } 15.
exd5 e5 16. Qe4 f5 17. Qd3 e4
{ The most precise way since White has some sort of counterplay by pushing forward the d-pawn. }
18. Nxe4 fxe4 19. Qxe4 Qd6
{ White's 3 pawns for the piece don't even feel as they are blocked. Black should be technically winning. }
