10. Nxb5 { Why is this natural looking move a mistake? } 10... Bd7 11. Nc3 Nb4
12. Qb3 a5 { Suddenly Black develops a very powerful initiative. } 13. Nxd5 a4
14. Nxf6+ gxf6
{ Much stronger than capturing with the queen, thus the White queen loses c3 as the retreat square, offering the queen trade. Please notice that the Black rook is also under attack on a8. }
15. Qc4 Rc8 16. Qe4+ Be7 { Black eventually crashes through. } 17. O-O-O Rxc2+
