[SetUp "1"]

{ Find a way to extinguish White's initiative on the kingside. } 17... Nh5
{ ...Nxf4 threat is inevitable. } 18. Qh4
{ This logical move actually is a blunder!   18.Qh3   Or  18.Qg4  - it's the same.  18...Nxf4!  19.Bxf4  e5  The entire point of the combination.  20.Qg3  exf4  21.Qxf4  Qa5  There's no more attack and White is left with some dark square weaknesses. }
18... Nxf4 19. Qxf4 { 19.Bxe7  Ng6  . } 19... f6 20. Bh4 g5
{ Not only does Black regain the piece, but also, Black dominates on the dark squares. }
